{"about_the_game":"&quot;Doodle adventure of Chameleon&quot; is a hand-drawn doodle-style <strong>hardcore</strong> side-scrolling platformer game. You'll play as a chameleon born from a young boy's imagination. By using your color-switching abilities, you can alter the elements of the game world as you navigate through different flat worlds, such as a sketchbook, a blackboard, and a storybook. As you tackle challenging levels, you'll gradually enter the boy's inner world and help him overcome the challenges of growing up.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Childhood hand-drawn doodle style</strong></h2><br>This game captures the brushstrokes of childhood doodles, taking you back to an imaginative time when you could savor the simple joys and dreams of your early years.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544900/extras/\u5f00\u573a\u52a8\u753b.gif?t=1717638105\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fun gameplay mechanics centered around color-changing</strong></h2><br>You need to make clever use of the chameleon's color-switching ability by freely switching between red, yellow, and blue colors to alter the elements in the game world. You must skillfully combine wall climbing, jumping, sprinting, and other actions to solve a series of puzzles.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544900/extras/\u53d8\u8272.gif?t=1717638105\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unique level settings and puzzles</strong></h2><br>As you progress through the levels and shift between the different flat worlds, new scene mechanics and puzzles will emerge, creating an enjoyable synergy with the color-switching gameplay. Enjoy the thrill of precise timing and route planning!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544900/extras/\u573a\u666f.gif?t=1717638105\" /><br><br>Additionally, the game features a chalkboard-style with chalk drawings and familiar elements such as math formulas, timetables, and classroom assignments. In these entertaining scenes, the chameleon embarks on a joyful adventure.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"I am a chameleon\uff01","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/34848e43a6f638470452c12065706fcb97ea9a18.jpg"},{"name":"Rich in Vitamin C","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/d78404fcf788dedab338246ac4a1439bfe88f614.jpg"},{"name":"An apple a day keeps the doctor away","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/1069fb68e21a18c719ef3abdb1afd364f04957e5.jpg"},{"name":"Apple medal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/32a0643affed0b610379b011094abe54c5b97a8a.jpg"},{"name":" The great illustrated crisis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/b822534f645e1b827bc4658acb9700b9edd3e090.jpg"},{"name":"Classes!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/318b8c69b59dcaab7029bfb534231332d4279ec6.jpg"},{"name":"The world of walls","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/e9333a39d14b2e064687217a8ed60d606b38e22d.jpg"},{"name":"Gamer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/e012b32811fa5bf9b7ee9127e592d408333b2985.jpg"},{"name":"Childhood dream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/02c885d1ffd901839b06fceaee006307215453e4.jpg"},{"name":"Wing win\uff01","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2544900/3edd0af203126d8dfca42f7f0f612a7cbbe4d323.jpg"}],"total":14},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1717638105","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic